draw_text(x,y, "This is a strange new world. There are noises you aren’t familiar with, and lots of strange creatures, probably. You might get eaten! A drop of water lands on your head. Then another, then a few more. The roof is so high above you, and it’s pouring water!")
draw_text(x,y, "You wander through this unfamiliar land. Your feet hurt, and it’s cold, and the roof is still upset with you. You’re wet, and you think you saw an animal. You wish you were home. Suddenly, you see something moving. You’re prepared to fight. You’ve never fought anything before. The creature reveals itself from the rubble around you, and instead of a horrible creature, you see a familiar sight.")


